HEADWORD: Raciness
<hw>Ra"ci*ness</hw> <pr>(r⟦amac⟧"s⟦icr⟧*n⟦ecr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The quality of being racy; peculiar and piquant flavor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The general characteristics of his [Cobbett's] style were
